  "prompt": "I am using Quora app. I need to answer the question as anonymous. How to do it?",
  "response": "To answer a question anonymously on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Open the Quora App**: First, open the Quora app on your smartphone.\n\n2. **Find the Question**: Navigate to the question you want to answer.\n\n3. **Tap on \u2018Answer\u2019**: Click on the \u2018Answer\u2019 button to start writing your response.\n\n4. **Write Your Answer**: Begin typing your answer in the text box provided.\n\n5. **Select Anonymous Mode**: Before submitting your answer, look for the \u201cAnonymous\u201d option. This is usually a toggle or button near the \u2018Submit\u2019 button. Tap on it to activate anonymous mode. \n\n6. **Submit Your Answer**: Once you're sure you want to post anonymously, click on \u2018Submit\u2019.\n\nNote: The steps might slightly vary based on the app version or updates. If you don\u2019t see the option, check for app updates or visit the Quora Help Center for the latest instructions.\n\nAdditionally, it's worth noting that posting anonymously might limit your ability to interact further as it\u2019s meant to protect your privacy.",
